            <h2>Design</h2>
            <p>With your own Webapp you have the ability to control the user experince from the ground up. You are not limited to one provider's platform and services, pick from a list of plug-ins and hope it gets what you need done. </p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#Design" role="button">Design &raquo;</a></p>
          </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
