            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Deployment&nbsp;<span class="text-muted">and Going "Live"</span></h2>
            <p class="lead">In deployment the website hostign server is prepared according to the needs of the site. the environment is configured for the expected traffic and proper credentials are put in place for the ability to use other cloud based services. The website is tested again to ensure that all functions are working as expected and the website renders correctly and when everything is done we celebrate the grand opening.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-5">
            <img class="featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto" data-src="holder.min.js/500x500/auto" alt="Generic placeholder image">
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="featurette-divider">

